<h3>Product Overview</h3>
<p>A complete game server hosting platform consisting of three integrated components:</p>
<ul>
<li><span>•</span> <strong>Control Plane:</strong> Microservices-based backend managing provisioning, orchestration, billing, and user management</li>
<li><span>•</span> <strong>Distributed Agents:</strong> Cross-platform workers (Linux + Windows) that provision and manage game servers</li>
<li><span>•</span> <strong>Unified Web Application:</strong> Blazor WASM frontend providing real-time console, server management, and administrative controls</li>
</ul>
